quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  26,2,∆äen ko Aayeeje Deftere …ďanngunde nden
  26,3,Belajo'o an a tampiniray hoore maa…óa kin fii …ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe
  26,4,Si Men Muuyii Men jippinay e ma…ď…ďe immorde ka kammu Aaya daa…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen √Īalla ko …óe yankinanii…óe mo
  26,5,Arataa e ma…ď…ďe waaju immorde ka Hinnorante On fu…ó…óaangu si wanaa …ďe laatike …óuurii…ďe ngu
  26,6,Gom…óii …ďe fennii aroyay e ma…ď…ďe kabaruuji ko …ďe laatinoo ko…ďe jalkitano
  26,7,"Enee, …ďe yi'aali faade e leydi ndin, no foti hewde ko Men fu…óini e mayri immorde e kala noone teddu…óo"
  26,8,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,9,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo On"
  26,10,"JaŇčto tuma nde Joomi maa…óa noddunoo Muusaa, …óum woni aru e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  26,11,"Yim…ďe Fir'awna, kaa on hulataa"
  26,12,"O maaki: \"Joom am , min mi…óo huli wata …ďe fennam"
  26,13,"∆Āernde am nden …ďittoo hara …óemngal am ngal wellitaaki, awa Nulu Haaruuna"
  26,14,No woodani …ďe e dow am bakkaatu mi…óo huli fii wata …ďe waram
  26,15,"O Daali: \"Wanaa non, yahee onon …ói…óo, Men…óen wonndi e moo…óon ko Men he…óii…ďe"
  26,16,"Aree ka Fir'awna wi'on: \"Menen dey ko men Nulaa…ďe Jooma winndere nden"
  26,17,∆äum woni accitu …ďi…ó…ďe Isra'iila …ďen wonndude e amen
  26,18,"O wi'i: \"Enee, men ne'aano ma ka amen …óoo hari ko a boobo, √Īii…ďu…óaa ka amen …óoo duu…ďi e ngurndam maa…óam"
  26,19,"Gollu…óaa gollal maa…óa ngal golluno…óaa ngal, an ko e yeddu…ďe …ďen jeya…óaa"
  26,20,"O maaki: \"Mi wa…óii …óum, ontuma hara min ko mi jeyaa…óo e majju…ďe …ďen"
  26,21,"Mi dogi on, tuma nde mi hulunoo on, Joomi am okkin mi Ganndal O wa…óin mi jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďen"
  26,22,"∆äum ko neema mo wajitirtaa mi …óum, fii a maccin…óinii …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen"
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko hommbo jeyi winndere nden"
  26,24,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike yananaa…ďe"
  26,25,"O wi'ani …ďen wonu…ďe banŇče makko: \"Enee; on he…óataako"
  26,26,"O maaki: \"Joomi moo…óon e Jooma baabiraa…ďe ardii…ďe …ďen"
  26,27,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Pellet, Nulaa…óo moo…óon on Nulaa…óo faade e moo…óon ko o feetu…óo"
  26,28,"O maaki: \"Ko Jooma funnaange e hirnaange e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si on laatike hakkiloo…ďe"
  26,29,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Mi woondii si jogitike rewetee…óo tanaa am, mi wa…óete jeyaa…óo dummbaa…ďe …ďen"
  26,30,"O maaki: \"Enee, hay si mi addanii ma huunde …ďanngunde"
  26,31,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Awa addu …óum, si tawii ko e goongu …ďen jeyaa…óaa"
  26,32,"O werliiii tuggordu makko ndun, jaka ko ndu biidaande(ngoolwa) …ďannguba"
  26,33,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo rawnungo wonannde ndaaroo…ďe …ďen"
  26,34,"[Fir'awna] wi'ani mbatu ngun fee makko: \"Pellet, oo…óoo ko mbileejo heewu…óo ganndal"
  26,35,Himo faandii yaltinirgol on ka leydi moo…óon mbilewu makko ngun. Ko hun…óun yamir…óon
  26,36,"∆Āe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musi…ó…óo makko on, nulaa e ca'e …óen moo…ďoo…ďe (mbile)"
  26,37,∆Āe addane kala mbileejo anndu…óo
  26,38,Mbilee…ďe …ďen moo…ďaa fii fodoore √Īalaande anndaande
  26,39,"Yim…ďe …ďen wi'anaa: \"Taw si onon ko on moo…ďike(ndenndi)"
  26,40,"Belajo'o menen men jokkay mbilee…ďe …ďen, si …ďe laatike ko kam…ďe woni foolu…ďe …ďen"
  26,41,"Tuma nde mbilee…ďe …ďen arunoo; …ďe wi'ani Fir'awna: \"Enee, hara no woodani men njo…ďdi si tawii ko men woni foolu…ďe …ďen"
  26,42,"O wi'i : \"Eyyo, haray ontuma on jeyaama e …ďa…ótinaa…ďe …ďen"
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani …ďe: \"mbeddee, ko werloton kon"
  26,44,"∆Āe li…ďi …ďokkoy ma…ď…ďe koy e cawoy ma…ď…ďe kon, …ďe wi'i: \"Sabu teddungal Fir'awna, ko menen woni fooloo…ďe …ďen"
  26,45,"Muusaa werlii tuggordu makko ndun, tawi kayru hindu mo…óa ko …ďe fefindii kon"
  26,46,Mbilee…ďe …ďen suuyi …ďe sujji
  26,47,"∆Āe wi'i : \"Men gom…óinii Jey…óo Winndere nden"
  26,48,Jey…óo Muusaa e Haaruuna
  26,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, on gom…óinay mo, ko adii mi duŇčanaade on? Pellet, ko kanko woni maw…óo moo…óon anndin…óo on on mbilewu ngun, kono aray anndon, mami ta∆īu juu…óe moo…óon e koy…óe moo…óon [ta∆īa] luutindira. Mami fetu on, on fow moo…óon"
  26,50,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Tanaa alaa, menen ko faade ka Joomi amen men ruttotoo"
  26,51,"Menen me…óen tam∆īinii nde Joomi amen yawtani men goopi amen …óin,tawde men laatike adii…ďe gom…óinnde …ďen"